ygData.subject: Re: Giant fire beetle?
ygData.msgSnippet: Unless I am mistaken, since it was quite awhile ago when I was traveling to Queynos, we came across and killed Giant Fire Beetles in the karanas where the hill
ygData.messageBody:
Unless I am mistaken, since it was quite awhile ago when I was traveling to
Queynos, we came across and killed Giant Fire Beetles in the karanas where
the hill giants and griffawns, griffenes and griffens play. They carry a
blue eye instead of the red eye normal fire beetles carry. Perhaps these
were just giant beetles, I'm not certain since as I said, it was very long
ago (we were level 18 about) that we encountered and fought them in our
travels.

Mikaela Tristram of The Rathe
